 What is this?
 -------------
 
      It's a console bash/awk script for preparing system configuration of Debian Lenny for installing
    Fantomas Iptconf.



 What's required for it work?
 ----------------------------

    - Debian Lenny installed standard system;
    - Network configured and Internet access for quering online repo's;
    
 
 How to use it?
 --------------

    Just run like this: 

	./debsysconf


 Sintax:
 -------
 
    debsysconf [--mysqlpass=<value>] [--fixrepo]
    
    Options:
      --mysqlpass=<value> - password that will be use as root password in MySQL server installing.
      --fixrepo - fix file /etc/apt/sources.list: comment all uncommented lines and put config links for
        Debian Lenny online repositories.
      






